      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>it's just hard to see it that way. i see the look on their faces when they have to drive me back from the doctors, the exhaustion in their eyes. i've always been the one taking care of everyone, and now i'm just the reason they're tired. it feels like the most loving thing i could do is just... stop making them deal with me. like, wouldn't they be more at peace if they didn't have to worry about me anymore?",
