    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but putting it that way just makes me feel more guilty. i'm still the one causing the stress, regardless of how they feel about it. i've been thinking about how much easier their lives would be if they didn't have to spend their weekends managing my medications or worrying about my falls. it almost feels selfish to keep dragging this out when i know it's just draining them. wouldn't it be more selfless to just let them go be happy without me clinging on?",
